Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的命運究竟是否在由看不見的力量或法則來掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  至少有一點很明確
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能加入我們  Guts！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺傷了我  又對我假施善心！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍來一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡用武力來解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都會得到自己想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了你的傲慢自大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我噁心！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不一般呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢說我用這把劍可以劈斷鋼鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他卻能輕易躲過了我的每次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只用單手使用那把細劍！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是個了不起的戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你願意  我可以等你傷癒之後再戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會贏的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會擊敗你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用點力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是不長記性  又在挑戰Griffith了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corkus  站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Griffith的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不許介入！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是個除掉他的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候輪到你發號施令了  Corkus？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許違抗Griffith的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到他了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣賞你的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用各種手段來擊敗你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不動的話你也使不了劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這麼僵持下去我也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘮嘮叨叨的真是很煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥的時候，你的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該像這樣用！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒見過Griffith被打翻在地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的血味道如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打賭你那張漂亮的臉蛋從沒挨過打！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實打得我夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的認輸  否則我就會折斷你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們的Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像你  Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這手下敗將！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好可憐呀  是不是已經絕望了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起他是鷹之團的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith從來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒對任何人說過這麼親切的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鷹之團在戰場上戰無不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有了死神這樣的綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不必擔心他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們都屬於Midland軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且  僱傭兵也沒有火炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要是他們再這樣下去並取得國王信任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就會失去現在的地位  名譽和尊嚴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頭疼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全擊敗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在做夢吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講起話來很親切  而且笑起來像個純真的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻毫不猶豫地扭住我的肩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在拆洋娃娃的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要殺他嗎  Corkus？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要前功盡棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有7個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說過不喜歡他的  沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  這個小鬼殺了Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他太厲害了  而且精通劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  就連Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會趁他不備時拿下他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  他現在受傷了也就拿不了劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等把他的屍體拋進樹林之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會讓Griffith相信他是逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群人可比不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sam  你先上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從來不先上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好別這麼干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就算受傷了，也還是比你們厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒要看個究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的回到你們的帳篷裡去  Corkus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska  為什麼你要保護他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他睡了兩個晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你對他會有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就砍掉你的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開-開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我欠你兩次人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我應該謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是執行Griffith的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則  我才不會管你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盼著你再打仗時趕緊死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座山上  敵人的總部有2000名士兵把守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務是要燒燬他們在後山的供應和其他一些補給品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來講  敵人都回重兵把守前山以防夜襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰術是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沿河岸行軍以便看起來像是在繞行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們要嘗試從敵人背後發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成任務之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要取捷徑而回  從敵軍的正中央突圍！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從敵人中央突破？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有後援嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說不會派遣部隊來參加夜襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是一群膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後衛就由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你來擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要協助所有同伴逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時還要在叢林的小道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖住敵方數量眾多的騎兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能勝任嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是命令  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith想試試那孩子的本領
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的傢伙  我估計他會死得很難堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒準會開溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith可不會用這樣的重任來試探我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith真的很信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我可不愁殺他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們是在河中行軍而不是按照預定的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不管走哪條路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也想不到我們會趟過急流發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會壓過我們行軍的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  當我們從背面放火時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢還可以借助風向擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一步都盡在他的掌握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼可怕的夜裡還要放哨真是太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們  連狼也不會在這樣的晚上出來活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵-敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他他們怎麼會從這個方向衝過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵-敵人來襲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火藥庫著火了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和他們玩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一字形突圍！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力脫出！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢看起來要順著風勢蔓延到總部了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把重騎兵推前！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幾個僱傭兵攻破總部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我們騎士來說簡直是個奇恥大辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前可沒見過這麼高效率的突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  該看我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我-我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  再快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得好  Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一個月之內是不會輕舉妄動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有些事情要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢擺出這麼無禮的態度！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的損失如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值一提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了我們的強力後衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人根本就靠近不了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在那樣狹窄的林間小道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己就能應付一群騎兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是有本領
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricket！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他先讓我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候返回了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我的手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放跑他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別講話！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會咬著舌頭的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去可不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人太重了  會被抓住的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持住！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要穿過樹林了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤-撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  Guts的戰鬥方式真是令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如Griffith想的  他真是說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  哪兒也不見Guts的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Griffith有著出色的領導才能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊的人也都完全相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  他有著完美的判斷力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼時候該採取什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不僅僅像是一個僱傭兵的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這上邊吹涼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你我才能及時逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ricket
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見過除了Griffith以外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼出色的戰士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只做了我該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼值得好謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我不是來和你討論這事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得跟我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚會缺了主角可不熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底下正在開慶功會  也算是歡迎你的宴會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我-我可沒讓你們這麼做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來，你個大頭混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Pippon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽著！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們乾杯來祝賀我們的新英雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被正式接納了  新兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真叫人吃驚呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量那麼懸殊的情況下還能獨自擋住敵人的進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正像Griffith預料的  你真是說到做到呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你有點混，可是我更喜歡你跟我們在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好樂樂吧  新兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有時永遠也無法獲得解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尋求寬恕的過程中，個人的贖罪注定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要隨著時光流逝而生活在痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是預示著未來的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是隱藏在過去的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個才更痛苦？
